{"tid":448142,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[加拿大]有冇上網卡有埋通話？","createTime":"2017-10-26T03:09:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-26T19:52:10.000Z","uid":54437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b165ceef4f65f0fcfcb64baa67d2e65b616a5bce","tid":448142,"uid":54437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T03:09:34.000Z","msg":"遲啲去加拿大，研究緊到時點樣可以上網同打電話<br />\n<br />\nGoolge到好似有隻T-mobile 嘅30日上網卡，但就見佢話唔包通話<br />\n<br />\n我想搵張有埋當地電話號碼，可以打出打入，方便到時聯絡當地啲親戚<br />\n<br />\n香港有冇啲咁嘅卡買？定話過到去先搵會易啲？<br />\n印象中加拿大啲通訊都幾落後(比起香港啦，見親戚啲電話plan都好落後)，應該難啲買到？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d05a7384586dac7dc9b1c7afd64de839f5c6b40","tid":448142,"uid":54437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T04:36:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7e367f1b909035f99563c8442f7a40b180de5269","tid":448142,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T04:44:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://abphy.com/media/BOfCjusA-RC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fabphy.com%2Fmedia%2FBOfCjusA-RC&d=myV3ArmkQETIy5dlh0Xiu49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=b898cabe\" target=\"_blank\">https://abphy.com/media/BOfCjusA-RC</a><br />\n<br />\n用過呢張<br />\n美加墨三國"},{"pid":"060308ae975365fbc440620c71d26f2275c0f3e4","tid":448142,"uid":24513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T04:58:10.000Z","msg":"用緊chatr<br />\n310蚊hkd一個月 得2gb 3g data<br />\n無限打+sms<br />\n樓上果個好似好抵"},{"pid":"4cfdd0fe4fdf89b9bdd92357257961bff00c7866","tid":448142,"uid":54437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T06:53:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://abphy.com/media/BOfCjusA-RC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fabphy.com%2Fmedia%2FBOfCjusA-RC&d=myV3ArmkQETIy5dlh0Xiu49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6w